creator: AXA Schweiz
descriptionHtml:
Your digital insurance card and helper when something happens – call AXA in case of an emergency, transmit your GPS location, and get help via the 24-hour hotline. The app also allows to access all contracts, documents, personal advisors, as well as notification of damage to vehicles, travel, personal liability, legal protection, or health.

Access to contracts and documents is optimized for private individuals – it can be used by private customers or insured persons in a pension fund... and you will never forget your myAXA password again. Simply and securely stay logged in!
descriptionShort: Your helper when something happens: assistance, claim, contracts, documents

Thank you for using MyAXA.

The app also allows to access all contracts, documents, personal advisors, as well as notification of damage to vehicles, travel, personal liability, legal protection, or health.

Access to contracts and documents is optimized for private individuals – it can be used by private customers or insured persons in a pension fund... and you will never forget your myAXA password again. Simply and securely stay logged in!
descriptionShort: Your helper when something happens: assistance, claim, contracts, documents
